    "en": {
      "title": "Authorities concerned over rising egg & chicken prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankan authorities have shown concern over the rising prices of eggs and chicken in the local market, said Minister Nalin Fernando.",
        "He said that instructions were given to the Consumer Affairs Authority to inquire into the price increase and provide him with a report.",
        "He said that financial facilities are to be provided to the poultry producers for the importation of animal feed."
      ],
